Note: <param> indicates a parameter to be replaced, [ arg ] indicates an optional argument.

To compile drsed:

	% make -f Makefile.<platform> DRSDIR=<directory containing libdrs.a> INCDIR=<directory containing drscdf.h>


To install the executable in directory INSTALL_DIR:

	% make -f Makefile.<platform> INSTALL_DIR=<installation directory> install

To execute drsed:

	% drsed [DRS-dictionary-file]

Type 'help' within drsed for more information.
